{"word":"Ἀμάριος","slug":"Ἀμάριος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n4957\" key=\"*)ama/rios\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Ἀμάριος</orth>, fem. <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Ἀμαρία</orth>, epith. of Zeus and Athena in Achaea, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ SIG\">SIG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">490</biblScope> </bibl> (Orchomenus in Arcadia, <date TEIform=\"date\">iii B. C.</date>), cf. <bibl n=\"http://www.trismegistos.org/text/75945\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Sammelb.\">Sammelb.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">357</biblScope> </bibl> (<placeName TEIform=\"placeName\">Egypt</placeName>): —<orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Ἀμάριον</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen>, precinct at Aegium in which the Achaean League met, prob. l. in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0099.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:7:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Str.\">Str.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.7.3</biblScope> </bibl> and <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0099.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5</biblScope> </bibl> (but <sense id=\"n4957.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">Ὁμάριον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0543.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:93:10\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plb.\">Plb.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.93.10</biblScope></bibl></cit>, hence <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ἀμάριος</foreign> prob. <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">Ὁμάριος, Ὁμαγύριος</ref> </xr> (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀμαρεῖν, ἁμαρτῆ</foreign>), and is not connected with <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀμάρα</foreign> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">ἡμέρα</ref> </xr>).</sense> </entryFree>"}]}